    "scenes": [
        
        {
            "id": "s1",
            "bg_color": "#993333",
            "text": {
                "header": "PYM Approvals",
                "body": "<p>Every now and then, your recommended media plan might have a pricing approval issue. Hey, it happens! If that happens, you'll submit your plan to PYM for approval through Slingshot. But what happens after that?</p><p>Move the timeline from left to right to see the basic steps for pricing approval</p>",
                "class": "align-center-wide"
            },
            "interaction": {
                "name": "cr_pym_s1",
                "id": "cr-pym-s1",
                "type": "clickReveal",
                "items": [
                    {
                        "header": "Step 1",
                        "body": "<p>When you submit an order for PYM approval, Slingshot generates a Salesforce approval case. This is what alerts PYM that your plan need their attention.</p>"
                    },
                    {
                        "header": "Step 2",
                        "body": "<p>You might need to revise your plan a few times for PYM to approve it. Any following submissions or resubmissions go to the same approval case. And each new submission becomes a new comment. This makes it easy for PYM to track what's been going on with your plan.	</p>"
                    },
                    {
                        "header": "Step 3",
                        "body": "<p>Congrats! Your plan's approved and the Export feature has unlocked! Now, you can export your media plan to the client! You can also generate an insertion order or submit an insertion order for approval.</p>"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "enter": [
                {
                    "id": "cr-pym-s1",
                    "type": "from",
                    "duration": 0.5,
                    "startTime": 0.3,
                    "props": {
                        "autoAlpha": 0
                    }
                },
                {
                    "id": "cr-pym-s1 .reveal-item",
                    "type": "staggerFrom",
                    "duration": 0.3,
                    "startTime": 0.8,
                    "staggerOffset": 0.15,
                    "props": {
                        "autoAlpha": 0
                    }
                }
            ],
            "leave": [
                {
                    "id": "cr-pym-s1",
